| `id`, `name` | Required |
| `order` | Optional display sort (activates drag-reorder in CRUD) |
| `description`, `prompt_negative` | Prompt content |
| `regenerate_images` / `regenerate` | Scheduler regeneration flag |
| `active_map_run_id` | Active batch run reference |
| `img2img_frame_id`, `img2img_frame_filename` | Img2Img source frame |
| `cnmap_frame_id`, `cnmap_frame_filename` | ControlNet map source frame |

#### Per-Entity Gallery Views

Each entity exposes a `v_gallery_{entity}` database view that joins `frames` with entity metadata for gallery display. `[VERIFY: definitions not included in source dump]`

