- The `genvideo_queue.sh` worker does not yet use the `worker_img_provider_default` DB config system — its provider (Pollinations `wan-fast`) and dimensions are hardcoded. [VERIFY — may be intentional or pending update]
- The `?embed=1` query parameter sets `initial-scale=0.8` (same value as standalone, so functionally identical in current code — `$viewportScale` is set to `0.8` in both branches). [VERIFY — likely a remnant or placeholder for a future differentiated embed scale]
