### UI & Interaction

#### Layout

```
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Topbar: hamburger | project name | btn strip          │  ~60px
├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Status bar: PyAPI dot | canvas/fps meta               │  ~24px
├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Chain Track (scrolls horizontally)                    │  200px
│  [Slot 0] ──[Transition Pill]── [Slot 1] ──… [+]     │
├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Detail Panel (scrollable)                             │  flex
│  Empty state  OR  Transition grid  OR  Slot settings  │
├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ FIXED PARAMS PANEL (always visible at viewport bottom)│  210px
│  Header: title | Browse Renders | Render | Save       │
│  Body: connector params (dur/intensity/easing/seed)   │
│         OR slot params (trim/speed)                   │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

The fixed params panel is pinned at the bottom of the viewport (`position: fixed`) with `--params-h: 210px` reserved via `padding-bottom` on the workspace. This ensures parameter controls are always reachable on mobile without scrolling.

#### Selection Model
- Tapping a **slot card** selects it → shows slot detail in scroll area + slot params in fixed panel (cyan `--acc3` border)
- Tapping a **connector pill** (not the action buttons) selects it → shows transition grid in scroll area + connector params in fixed panel (amber `--acc` border)
- Tapping outside deselects → empty state shown in both areas

#### Connector Actions (inline on connector)
Each connector exposes two inline buttons without requiring selection:
- **Render** — queues an immediate render job
- **Play** — appears only when `job_video_id` exists; opens preview modal

#### Key Modals

| Modal | Trigger | Content |
|---|---|---|
| Video Picker | "+ Slot" button or chain "+" | Four-tab fly-out (Tree/Seq/Fuzz/Storyboard) with paginated video grid |
| Projects | Folder icon / hamburger sidebar | Paginated project list + inline create form |
| Edit Project | Gear icon | Canvas W/H, FPS, name |
| Render Jobs | Film icon | Last 30 jobs with status badges and preview links |
| Browse Renders | "Browse Renders" in params header | Two-tab demo browser (By Type / This Slot) |
| Preview | Render complete / Play button | `<video>` element with controls |

#### Mobile-First Behaviour
- Viewport meta set to `maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no, viewport-fit=cover`
- Chain track scrolls horizontally with thin scrollbar (`scrollbar-width: thin`)
- Video picker tree panel slides in as a drawer on viewports < 700px, with a backdrop overlay
- All `<input type="number">` and text inputs have `-webkit-user-select: text; touch-action: auto` to restore native mobile text selection
- `select` elements have `-webkit-user-select: auto` for the same reason
- Hover-only elements (slot delete button, slot action buttons) are made persistently visible on `hover: none` devices

#### Real-time Feedback
- PyAPI status dot polls every 30 seconds; changes colour (green = online, red = offline)
- Render polling runs at 2.5-second intervals; connector pill dot updates colour (working = amber pulse, done = green, fail = red)
- Toast notifications confirm all async actions (save, queue, completion, error)

