### Dependencies & Related Modules

| Dependency | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| FastAPI PyAPI (`main.py`) | Runtime | Service registration via `serv.conf.json`; MuviTriccs registered as active service with prefix `/muvitriccs` |
| OpenCV (`cv2`) | Python | All frame manipulation, warping, blurs |
| NumPy | Python | Array operations throughout transition family renderers |
