- **Thumbnail generation** in `registerTransitionVideo` uses PHP GD (`imagecreatetruecolor`) to produce a placeholder 320×180 JPEG. No actual video frame is extracted for the thumbnail. `[VERIFY]` whether a FFmpeg-based thumbnail (first-frame extract) is planned as a replacement.

- **`video_counter` table** is referenced in `registerTransitionVideo` for sequential video filename generation (`video0000001.mp4` style). This is a shared counter across all SAGE video-producing modules. Concurrent renders could theoretically race on this counter, though in solo-operator use this is not a practical concern.

