### Known State / Notes

- **`note` field unused in UI:** `boards_items.note` (production notes) is stored and retrieved in `fetch_board_content` as `production_note` but is not rendered anywhere in the current frontend. Likely planned for a future inline annotation feature. `[VERIFY]`

