| **Frames / Image Generation** | Source of all frame records. Storyboard frames reference `frames.id`. |
| **Showrunner / Auto-Narrative Lab** (`narratives_v11.php`) | Target of "Clone to Narrative" action; new `narrative_sequences` record is created and the user is redirected there. |
| **ScrollMagic Multi-PRM** (`view_scrollmagic_multi_prm.php`) | Can receive a storyboard ID for multi-plane viewing. |
| **Entity Form** (`entity_form.php`) | Loaded in an iframe within SbCut''s entity details modal. |
| **VidBat** | May display storyboard-associated frames for video review; [VERIFY] whether storyboard IDs are passed to VidBat. |
| **SAGE GearMenu** (`ModuleRegistry`, `gear_menu_globals.js`) | Mounted on frame grids in both detail views. |
| **SAGE ImageEditor** (`ModuleRegistry`) | Mounted in both detail views; accessible via GearMenu actions. |
| **StoryboardHelper** (`StoryboardHelper.php`) | PHP helper class encapsulating the `importFramesToStoryboard()` logic called by `storyboard_import.php`. |
| **`sketch_migration_entities` / `sketch_migration_frames`** | Internal de-duplication tables used only by `clone_to_narrative`. [VERIFY these are created in schema] |

