| MultiVid 2.5D compositor | Related compositing tool — parallel pipeline for 2.5D multiplane video (separate module) |

---

## Asset Linker: `view_motani_add.php`

This is a lightweight companion utility page for manually linking existing frames, videos, and meshes to an animatic record. It is not integrated into the Motion Editor UI directly but is the primary admin tool for populating the three join tables (`animatic_frames`, `animatic_videos`, `animatic_meshes`) that the Motion Editor reads on load.

It accepts a POST form with `animatic_id`, `frame_id`, `video_id`, and `mesh_id` (all optional except `animatic_id`). Each non-zero asset ID is validated against its source table before being inserted. Uses `INSERT IGNORE` to prevent duplicates. Renders feedback as success/error messages inline.

