- `ssh_password` parameter in `RunJobRequest` is reserved but not currently wired into the `SCPDestination` constructor beyond storage. Key-based auth via Termux''s `~/.ssh/` is the expected default. [VERIFY]
- The `schedule_hint` field is display-only; no automated scheduler trigger exists in the current codebase dump. [VERIFY — confirm if Scheduler Forge integration is planned]
- A CLI Forge Hub recipe for backup jobs is not present in this dump. [VERIFY whether one exists or is planned]
- The `statRuns` header counter reflects runs created today based on `created_at` local time parsing in the browser, not a server-side count.
- Temp archives are written to `{PROJECT_ROOT}/temp/` during execution and cleaned up in `finally` blocks regardless of run outcome.
- The `backup_runs` table has reached run ID 248 at time of this documentation, indicating active production use.
