| `run_extraction` | Streamed SSE-style response. Extracts mentions from all enabled sources, writes `fuzz_queue`, submits async clustering job to tablet PyAPI via `PyApiFuzzService::clusterAsync()`. Returns `JOB_ID:` token. |
| `get_extraction_job_status` | Proxies job status from tablet PyAPI. |
| `apply_clusters` | Fetches completed clusters from tablet PyAPI; triggers local ingest job via `PyApiLocalIngestService::startIngest()`. |
