The tablet PyAPI URL is resolved via `WORDNET_PYAPI_URL` env var (default `http://127.0.0.1:8009`). [VERIFY: exact env var name used by `PyApiFuzzService` vs `PyApiLocalIngestService` — confirm whether they both use the same base URL or separate env vars]

