|---|---|
| Knowledge Graph (`kg_view.php`, `kg_graph.php`) | Candidates are promoted/linked to `kg_nodes`. KG node search is used in the dossier link picker. The Fuzz Graph links out to `kg_graph.php`. |
| Entity Form (`entity_form.php`) | Source entity deep-dives open inside an iframe modal from both the Forge and the Landing page. |
