| Tablet PyAPI | Hosts `fuzz_service.py`. Receives TF-IDF clustering jobs from PHP via `PyApiFuzzService`. |
| Chroma vector DB | Queried via `PyApiVectorService` for semantic candidate search against the `sage_sketches_nu` collection. |
| Dashboard | Header back-link. The Forge is accessed from the SAGE dashboard module list. |

