| 🌀 | Control Deck | `/scheduler_runner.php` | Modal |
| 🧭 | Dashboard | `/dashboard.php` | Navigate |
| ⚗ | Gen Forge | `/generator_forge.php` | Modal |
| 🗺️ | Enhanimatics | `/enhanimaticism.php` | Navigate |
| 🛹 | Boards | `/boards_view.php` | Navigate |
| 🛢️ | DB Tool | `/dbtool.php` | Modal |
| 🎨 | Styles | `/styles_toggle.php` | Modal |
| 📋 | Clipboard | `/clipboard_manager.php` | Modal |
| 📊 | KG View | `/kg_view.php` | Navigate |
| 🪄 | Fuzz Forge | `/fuzz_forge.php` | Navigate |
| 📅 | Scheduler | `/view_queue.php` | Navigate |
| 🎬 | Video Rev | `/view_vidbat_review.php` | Navigate |
| 🎞 | Storyboards | `/view_storyboards.php` | Navigate |

---

#### Clipboard Manager (`clipboard_manager.php`)

| Feature | Description |
|---|---|
| **Standalone page** | Full-height, mobile-optimised layout. Designed for iframe embedding or direct access. |
| **`view_area` scoping** | All items scoped to a named area (e.g. `global`, `enhanimatics`). Validated against `^[a-z0-9_]{1,80}$`. Each area has independent pin state and sort order. |
| **Add clip** | Text + optional label. Max 4000 chars content, 120 chars label. Enter key submits (without Shift). |
| **Inline edit** | Click clip text to reveal textarea + label input. Save with Enter or `✓` button. Cancel with Escape or blur. |
| **Pin/unpin** | Toggles pin state via upsert on `clipboard_visibility`. Pinned items float to top. |
| **Delete** | Deletes `clipboard_items` row; cascade removes all `clipboard_visibility` rows. Confirm dialog before deletion. |
| **Drag-to-reorder** | SortableJS on the item list. `sort_order` persisted per `view_area`. |
| **Copy to clipboard** | `navigator.clipboard.writeText()` via event delegation. Graceful error toast if API unavailable. |
| **Parent notification** | After any mutation, fires `window.parent.postMessage({ type: ''clipboard_updated'', ... }, ''*'')` so the Forge Tool panel can react. |

---

#### Control Deck (`scheduler_runner.php`) — "Control Deck v5"

The Control Deck is a curated task-launcher UI that sits between the user and the raw `scheduled_tasks` table. It manages a layer of **wrappers** (`task_wrappers`) — each wrapper is a named, icon-labelled button pinned to a specific task ID with a fixed argument set. Clicking a wrapper button sets `run_now = 1` on the underlying `scheduled_tasks` row and injects the wrapper''s `fixed_args`, triggering the platform''s scheduler daemon to execute the corresponding shell script.

| Feature | Description |
|---|---|
| **Wrapper grid** | Ordered list of `task_wrappers` rows rendered as icon + title + summary pill + run button + edit button. Ordered by `display_order ASC, id DESC`. |
| **Run button** | Fires `run_wrapper` AJAX action. Sets `scheduled_tasks.run_now = 1` and `args = fixed_args` for the linked task. Button shows ⏳ with green pulse animation during request. |
| **Live log console** | Expandable bottom-sheet style log panel at the top of the page. Contains a `<select>` populated with up to 50 recent `.log` files (filtered: excludes `err*` and `*_exit.log`). Log content polled every 2 seconds via `scheduler_log_fetch.php`. File list polled every 4 seconds. Auto-scroll checkbox. |
| **Auto log switch** | When a run button is pressed, `pendingAutoSwitch = true`. On the next file list poll, if a new `task_run_*_out.log` file appears, the console automatically switches to it and opens the panel. |
| **Manual log select** | Changing the log file dropdown auto-expands the console and immediately fetches content. |
| **Console expand/collapse** | Clicking the console header toggles the log box via CSS height/opacity animation. Chevron rotates 90° when open. |
| **Add Preset** | `+` row at the bottom of the wrapper list opens the CRUD modal for creating a new wrapper. |
| **Edit Preset modal** | Full CRUD modal (name, icon, summary, fixed args, display order, linked task). "Copy Default" link copies the linked task''s current default `args` into the fixed args field. |
| **Delete Preset** | Available in edit modal via a `Delete` button (confirm dialog). Removes the wrapper row; does not affect the underlying `scheduled_tasks` row. |
| **Full Scheduler link** | Header button links to `scheduler_view.php` for the complete scheduler management interface. |

---


