- **AG graph is fully rebuilt on every Aggregate run** — all `ag_nodes` and `ag_node_items` for a document are deleted before re-insertion. This ensures idempotency but means any manual AG edits will be overwritten on the next aggregate run for that document (unless `is_locked` is set).

