The `ie-fullscreen` CSS variant on `#ieModalContainer` removes all border-radius and margin for the DAW view.

#### Responsive / Mobile Behaviour

- Shot grid: `auto-fill minmax(160px, 1fr)` — adapts from ~2 columns on phone to 4–5 on tablet.
