- Paradigm B: fixed `app-container` height with `flex: 1` scrollable script area; `60vh` bottom padding ensures last shot scrolls fully into view.
- Scene Playlist: `overflow: hidden` on body; aspect-ratio player + 180px scrollable playlist strip.

#### Toast Notifications

`js/toast.js` (Forge amber style) used throughout for save confirmations, order changes, and errors.

