### UI & Interaction

- **Layout:** Single-column workspace capped at `900px` with a sticky navbar. Mobile-first; all controls are touch-accessible.
- **Theme:** Forge UI — Space Mono (labels, nav, monospace elements) + Syne (body text); amber (`#f5a623`) accent; dark/light theme via `data-theme` attribute. PLUSH defines its own `--pl-*` CSS custom property set on top of the base theme.
- **Toast notifications:** All async operations surface success/warn/error toasts via `/js/toast.js`.
- **Modals:** New Story, System Languages, Entity Detail (iframe), and Color Picker are all implemented as fixed-position backdrop modals with click-outside-to-close.
