- **`delete_story` button in list view** has a commented-out earlier version of the button markup in the source alongside the live version. The live version uses `htmlspecialchars(json_encode(...))` for safe attribute encoding; the commented version used bare `json_encode`. No functional difference — cleanup pending. [VERIFY before release]
