### UI & Interaction

**Layout:** Full-viewport flex column (`height: 100dvh`). Panels from top: header bar → active forge filters bar → top list panel (scroll-capped) → mid config panel → frame grid (flex-grows) → footer action bar.

**Header:** Entity type dropdown (right-aligned). Title shows "✨ Entities Mode".

**Forge filters bar:** Shows active filter pills or an italic "No active Forge filters" placeholder. Pills have × close buttons.

**Top list panel:**
- Controls row: Map Run/Entity/Frame mode toggle, Forge Filter button, optional Create Entity button, search input, pagination (prev / page input / total / next)
- Optional entity sort bar (ID / Latest Frame) — shown in Entities and Frames modes
- Scrollable item list; in Frames mode the list is hidden and the grid is loaded directly

**Mid config panel:**
- Prompt input + Compose button
- Clipboard chips row + Manage button + Add Frames (+Frames) button
- Grid toolbar (two rows): info label + Select All/None/ScrollMagic link | Hide Imported, Hide Enhanced, Raw, 1Col, d2i, and entity-prompt checkboxes

**Frame grid:** `pswp-gallery` class enables PhotoSwipe lightbox on `<a class="f-link">` elements. Card labels toggle selection. In Frames mode, entity name is shown instead of frame ID in the label.

**Footer:** Selection count summary + STBA, Enhance Frames, Import to Animatics buttons (disabled when count = 0).

**Modals:**
- Frame viewer (full-screen iframe, `view_frame.php` or `entity_form.php`)
- Forge filter (slide-up bottom-sheet with sidebar + list)
- Quick Compose (slide-up bottom-sheet)
- Add Frames (slide-up bottom-sheet, two tabs)
- Storyboard Picker (slide-up bottom-sheet)

All bottom-sheet modals close on backdrop click and on `Escape` key.

**Mobile-first:** 2-column frame grid at base, auto-fill at ≥600px. Footer buttons expand at ≥600px. All panels are flex-direction column. Safe-area inset padding applied to footer.

**Theme:** Supports `data-theme="light"` toggled via `localStorage(''spw_theme'')` (applied by the Forge UI shell). Dark theme variables: `--bg: #0a0a0f`, `--card: #111118`, accent `--purple: #8b5cf6`, `--amber: #f59e0b`, `--teal: #14b8a6`.

**Toast notifications:** Uses `/js/toast.js` + `/css/toast.css`. Called via `Toast.show(message, type)`.

**Cross-frame messaging:** Listens for `clipboard_updated` `postMessage` events from the clipboard manager iframe to refresh chips without a page reload.

