## 5. API / Backend Integration

### `narratives_api_v11.php` (GET)

| Action | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `fetch_library` | Main paginated library load. Accepts `page`, `context_id`, `filter_payload`. Calls `buildRichQuery()` from helpers, then `VectorContextEngine::getRankedItems[Multi]()`, then `SketchLibrary::hydratePage()`. Returns debug log when `DEBUG_MODE = true`. |
| `hydrate_sequence` | Resolves `{sketch_id, frame_id}` array to full sketch data for timeline rebuild. |
| `get_filter_cats` | Returns fixed category list: `[''episodes'',''scene_hooks'',''characters'',''locations'',''factions'',''artifacts'']`. |
| `get_filter_items` | Returns entity names for a given doc and category via `LoreAccessService`. |
| `get_entity_preview` | Returns full structured entity data for the Peek modal. |

### `narratives_api_v11.php` (POST)

| Action | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `save_sequence` | Saves or updates a sequence in `narrative_sequences`. |

### `auto_narratives_api_v11.php` (POST)

| Action | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `generate_sequence` | Runs `AutoDirectorV11::generate()`; saves to `narrative_sequences_auto`; returns hydrated items. |
| `promote` | Promotes a pending auto sequence to `narrative_sequences`. |
| `delete` | Archives a pending auto sequence (`status = ''archived''`). |

### `auto_narratives_api_v11.php` (GET)

| Action | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `list_results` | Returns up to 50 non-archived auto sequences. |
| `get_filter_cats` | Same fixed category list as above. |
| `get_filter_items` | Entity names for a doc/category. |
| `get_entity_preview` | Peek modal data. |

### `filter_forge_api.php` (GET)

| Action | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `list_frames` | Primary Forge result set. Accepts all filter params; returns frame rows with optional membership flags. |
| `list_filter_options` | Autocomplete data for each filter picker (modes: `fuzz`, `doc`, `doc_entities`, `kg`, `seq`, `storyboard`, `entity`). |
| `check_membership` | Checks if frame IDs are in storyboards, narrative sequences, or KG. |
| `resolve_relationships` | BFS walk over KG edges from a given node; returns edge list and linked entity IDs. |

### PyAPI (Tablet)

`PyApiVectorService` is called for all ChromaDB queries. Queries target `sage_sketches_nu` with `n_results` between 50–250 depending on pool mode. The tablet PyAPI URL is resolved from the `WORDNET_PYAPI_URL` environment variable (default `http://127.0.0.1:8009`).

### AI Providers

| Config ID | Usage |
|-----------|-------|
| `auto_director_v1` | Per-shot next-step reasoning in AutoDirectorV11 (only when "Use AI" is checked) |
| `filter_query_enricher_v1` | Enriches raw lore query strings into semantically dense Chroma queries (always active when config is present, regardless of Director toggle) |

